PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532930\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532930\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 07, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vap1665702657514.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vap1665702657514.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vap1665702657514.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vap1665702657514\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                    \n Meta_Variant\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"vap1665702657514__meta_variant_193608\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Identifies the meta variant character set for which the current translation table is intended. It ensures that Uniface meta character definitions used in translation table definitions prior to Uniface 9 are automatically mapped to Unicode characters.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"vap1665702657514__topic_d64580e1_d64581e1_d64582e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vap1665702657514__p_d64583e1_d64584e1_d64585e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Variant</var>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">TableType</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vap1665702657514__topic_d42697e1_d42698e1_d42699e1_d42700e1_d42701e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1164471e68\">\n                     \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vap1665702657514__li_d28064e1_d28065e1_d28066e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Variant</var>—generic name for a character set, which may be implemented by one ore more platform-specific characters sets or code pages.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vap1665702657514__li_d28067e1_d28068e1_d28069e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">TableType</var>—mnemonic specifying the type of translation table; one of:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vap1665702657514__li_d28070e1_d28071e1_d28072e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">^display</code>—identifies a device translation table for a display device\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vap1665702657514__li_d28073e1_d28074e1_d28075e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">^printer</code>—identifies a device translation table for a printer device\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vap1665702657514__li_d28076e1_d28077e1_d28078e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">^keyboard</code>—identifies a keyboard translation table for a keyboard\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vap1665702657514__li_d28079e1_d28080e1_d28081e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">^dbms</code>—identifies a keyboard translation table for a database\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vap1665702657514__p_d64589e1_d64590e1_d64591e1\">If omitted, the current meta variant of the Uniface IDE is used for the mapping.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vap1665702657514__topic_d42702e1_d42703e1_d42704e1_d42705e1_d42706e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1164471e119\">\n                     \n Allowed Meta Variants\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_<var class=\"keyword varname\">Variant</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__3\">\n External Character Set\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Unicode</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__2\">\n Unicode\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__3\">\n UTF8\n <p class=\"p\">A subset is used for <code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_<var class=\"keyword varname\">Variant</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_0</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_Western</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__2\">\n Western\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__3\">\n LATIN! (DEC)\n                             <p class=\"p\">CP437 (IBMPC, PC)</p>\n<p class=\"p\">CP850</p>\n<p class=\"p\">AIX (IBMRT)</p>\n<p class=\"p\">EBCDIC</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_1</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_Japanese</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__2\">\n Japanese\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__3\">\n SJIS\n <p class=\"p\">EUC</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_2</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_Simplified_Chinese</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__2\">\n Simplified Chinese\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__3\">\n GB (GB2312)\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_3</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_Traditional_Chinese</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__2\">\n Traditional Chinese\n <p class=\"p\">(Traditional Chinese character sets are only partially implemented.)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__3\">\n BIG5\n <p class=\"p\">CNS (CNS11643)</p>\n<p class=\"p\">IBM5550</p>\n<p class=\"p\">ETEN</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_4</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_Korean</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__2\">\n Korean\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__3\">\n KSC (KSC5601)\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_5</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_Eastern_Europe</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__2\">\n Eastern European\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__3\">\n CP1250\n <p class=\"p\">LATIN2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_6</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_Cyrillic</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__2\">\n Cyrillic\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__3\">\n CP1251\n <p class=\"p\">LATIN5</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_7</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_Greek</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__2\">\n Greek\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__3\">\n CP1253\n <p class=\"p\">LATIN7</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_8</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_Hebrew</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__2\">\n Hebrew\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__3\">\n CP1255\n <p class=\"p\">LATIN8</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_9</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_Arabic</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__2\">\n Arabic\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vap1665702657514__table_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1__entry__3\">\n CP1256\n <p class=\"p\">LATIN6</p>\n<p class=\"p\">ARAIX</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vap1665702657514__topic_d42707e1_d42708e1_d42709e1_d42710e1_d42711e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1164471e477\">\n                     \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vap1665702657514__p_d64598e1_d64599e1_d64600e1\">Meta variants are internal character sets that are mapped to external character sets independently of the platform, for example <code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_Western</code> to identify character sets used for Western languages such as English, German, and Spanish.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vap1665702657514__p_d64601e1_d64602e1_d64603e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">meta_<var class=\"keyword varname\">Variant</var>\n</code> mnemonic ensures that Uniface meta character definitions (Font 0 through 7) used in translation table definitions prior to Uniface 9 are automatically mapped to Unicode characters. Uniface now uses Unicode as its internal character set rather than the meta character sets.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vap1665702657514__p_d64604e1_d64605e1_d64606e1\">It is also possible to create character set mappings in the <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gzx1665702657590.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gzx1665702657590.html\" title=\"Use the [META_CharSet ] section of the assignment file to map characters in the Uniface meta character set, for example [META_Japanese] or [META_Western], to and from Unicode.\">[META_CharSet]</a> sections of the assignment file.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zip1665702657738.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Meta Variants</a><p>A meta variant is an internal character set that is used to translate between Unicode and a supported external character set.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532930\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532930\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Meta_Variant Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 07, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Meta_Variant Identifies the meta variant character set for which the current translation table is intended. It ensures that Uniface meta character definitions used in translation table definitions prior to Uniface 9 are automatically mapped to Unicode characters. meta_ Variant TableType Arguments Variant —generic name for a character set, which may be implemented by one ore more platform-specific characters sets or code pages. TableType —mnemonic specifying the type of translation table; one of: ^display —identifies a device translation table for a display device ^printer —identifies a device translation table for a printer device ^keyboard —identifies a keyboard translation table for a keyboard ^dbms —identifies a keyboard translation table for a database If omitted, the current meta variant of the Uniface IDE is used for the mapping. Allowed Meta Variants meta_ Variant Description External Character Set Unicode Unicode UTF8 A subset is used for meta_ Variant meta_0 meta_Western Western LATIN! (DEC) CP437 (IBMPC, PC) CP850 AIX (IBMRT) EBCDIC meta_1 meta_Japanese Japanese SJIS EUC meta_2 meta_Simplified_Chinese Simplified Chinese GB (GB2312) meta_3 meta_Traditional_Chinese Traditional Chinese (Traditional Chinese character sets are only partially implemented.) BIG5 CNS (CNS11643) IBM5550 ETEN meta_4 meta_Korean Korean KSC (KSC5601) meta_5 meta_Eastern_Europe Eastern European CP1250 LATIN2 meta_6 meta_Cyrillic Cyrillic CP1251 LATIN5 meta_7 meta_Greek Greek CP1253 LATIN7 meta_8 meta_Hebrew Hebrew CP1255 LATIN8 meta_9 meta_Arabic Arabic CP1256 LATIN6 ARAIX Description Meta variants are internal character sets that are mapped to external character sets independently of the platform, for example meta_Western to identify character sets used for Western languages such as English, German, and Spanish. The meta_ Variant mnemonic ensures that Uniface meta character definitions (Font 0 through 7) used in translation table definitions prior to Uniface 9 are automatically mapped to Unicode characters. Uniface now uses Unicode as its internal character set rather than the meta character sets. It is also possible to create character set mappings in the [META_CharSet] sections of the assignment file. Related Links Meta Variants A meta variant is an internal character set that is used to translate between Unicode and a supported external character set. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}